# Copie para `.env` na raiz do GodManager e preencha.
# QuickBooks (Intuit Developer) — OAuth2
# 1) No portal Intuit (Keys & Credentials), copie Client ID e Client Secret (nunca commite o secret).
# 2) Em "Redirect URIs", adicione EXACTAMENTE o mesmo valor que QB_REDIRECT_URI (inclui http/https e path).
# 3) Sandbox: QB_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox e empresa de teste no QuickBooks Sandbox.
# 4) Produção: QB_ENVIRONMENT=production e QB_BASE_URL=https://quickbooks.api.intuit.com
QB_CLIENT_ID=
QB_CLIENT_SECRET=
QB_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3101/crm/integrations/quickbooks/callback
QB_ENVIRONMENT=sandbox
QB_BASE_URL=https://sandbox-quickbooks.api.intuit.com
